{"tid":1846101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［暉明邨隔離區］等我話你知，點解北區人咁大反應","createTime":"2020-01-27T13:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:20:54.000Z","uid":154627,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa67b670530f3dcbfb345ad2f92cc2fa46c8db9","tid":1846101,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"其他區可能唔明點解北區人咁大反應<br />\n但係請你睇下下圖<br />\n左係暉明邨(隔離點)右係雍盛苑，相距只有約三十米<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWHzqFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWHzqFE.png&h=1a3da273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再睇下google map ，紅圈係暉明邨<br />\n附近有幾間中學同多個大型屋邨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C9oZBNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC9oZBNC.png&h=7ecd35f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">！！係近到連google map都疊埋左！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者有人會覺得總要有地方要做隔離點，唔可以咁自私<br />\n係！岩！<br />\n我唔反對你係北區有隔離點，但絕對唔係咁撚近民居<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n街坊阿叔話：「對面暉明打個乞嗤都吹到黎我屋企」<br />\n新屋嶺(同屬北區)呢啲遠啲既地方我覺得可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過最撚緊要都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封關</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">希望大家唔好誤會北區人好自私<br />\n希望大家唔好誤會北區人好自私<br />\n希望大家唔好誤會北區人好自私</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9c6d7bebba8f1cf7c53da99a4e3c89a29de6d49","tid":1846101,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90b47883ec557c92349d8ecc93d69640cdf9b6c2","tid":1846101,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:15:13.000Z","msg":"九龍灣都有咁既情況，大家關注下我地"},{"pid":"25f5a85d1a506c5ae209838155246f7b225ef789","tid":1846101,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"支持醫護罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fedddba783c5be67c0855fa5b9b0a83822959c7","tid":1846101,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"元朗人表完全明白同支持。正常人都知唔可以搵個人煙咁密，咁近民居既位起"},{"pid":"84cc971000c3a55d5dcda05834f65851b9ec8a98","tid":1846101,"uid":154627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"封關！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}